title: Saleman Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 3 weeks. I interviewed at NADA (New Hampton, IA) in Aug 2020
Interview Descriptions: Called me up arranged a date, conducted interview went over me past work record and put several senioros to me I answered as honest as |I could, Then they gave me a chance to ask questions about the job and compaNY
Interview Questions: Experience, what I expected from the role and were I saw myself in 5 years

title: Janitor Interview
Application Type: I applied through an employee referral. I interviewed at NADA in May 2020
Interview Descriptions: Your experience and IQ. If your IQ is too good they will fail you. I had a good IQ for the job. The manager and the senior janitor will test you. They called me onsite for my work.
Interview Questions: What is 2^10? How did you get the answer?
